Package edu.wpi.first.units

Class Mass

java.lang.Object
edu.wpi.first.units.Unit<Mass>
edu.wpi.first.units.Mass
public class Mass extends Unit<Mass>
Unit of mass dimension.

This is the base type for units of mass dimension. It is also used to specify the dimension for Measure: Measure<Mass>.

Actual units (such as Units.Grams and Units.Pounds) can be found in the Units class.
